  ('1ac6f817-b151-482c-bb2c-7f4321d3237c', 'Conjugate the verb ''parler'' (to speak) in the present tense for ''tu'' (you informal)', 'tu parles', '{"parles"}'::text[], 'verb_conjugation:-er_verbs', 'beginner', 'conjugation', 'Regular -er verbs follow a pattern: remove -er and add endings. For ''tu'', add -es', '{"Remove the -er and add the ''tu'' ending","The ending for ''tu'' with -er verbs is -es"}'::text[], FALSE, NULL, '2026-02-01T09:13:02.750401+00:00', '2026-02-01T09:13:02.750401+00:00'),
