  ('271567c0-3b95-4b41-83ff-0cfb6d640eac', 'Conjugate the irregular verb ''aller'' (to go) in the present tense for all subject pronouns and write one sentence using it in the near future tense (futur proche).', 'je vais, tu vas, il/elle/on va, nous allons, vous allez, ils/elles vont. Je vais aller au cinéma demain.', '{"je vais, tu vas, il va, nous allons, vous allez, ils vont. Nous allons manger ce soir.","vais, vas, va, allons, allez, vont. Elle va partir bientôt."}'::text[], 'verb_conjugation:irregular_verbs', 'advanced', 'conjugation', 'Tests knowledge of the irregular verb ''aller'' and its use in forming the near future tense (aller + infinitive)', '{"''Aller'' is highly irregular - it doesn''t follow -er verb patterns","For near future: use ''aller'' conjugated + infinitive of another verb","Example structure: subject + aller + infinitive"}'::text[], TRUE, NULL, '2026-02-01T09:13:02.750401+00:00', '2026-02-01T09:13:02.750401+00:00'),
